snippet.title: New Mod: Psi (Early alpha commentary)
snippet.description:
Showing off Psi, my new mod. Very early! Will be out soon(tm). Yes, I did fix the bug I found at the end already, thanks :p
Sorry for any cuts in my voice. My microphone loves cutting off my voice when I'm not talking too loud. I'll have that fixed by next time.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Vazkii
